<p>In this final show of the year before heading off to San Francisco for Macworld Expo, John and Dave start by sharing the tips that they &#8212; and you! &#8212; have acquired over the years attending trade shows. Listen for advice from the pros on how to survive the big week! Then it&#8217;s on to questions, including topics such as wireless safety, disk buffers, large desktop folders, and more!</p>
